Paris: the city of love and light. On this leg of The Traveling Photographer, Strobist.com founder David Hobby explores the best of what Paris has to offer, from Montparnasse and the Eiffel Tower to the city's famous museums and street cafÃƒÂ©s. He also covers logistics for the photographer on the move, and tips for getting the most out of the "magic hour." This city-specific vignette will help make Paris much more accessible, productive, and enjoyable to the first-time photo traveler.

To make sure you're getting the most from this course and every other destination David visits, make sure to watch The Traveling Photographer: Fundamentals
